quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  6,125,"Ẹnikẹ́ni tí Allāhu bá fẹ́ fọ̀nà mọ̀, Ó máa ṣí igbá-àyà rẹ̀ payá fún ’Islām. Ẹnikẹ́ni tí Ó bá sì fẹ́ ṣì lọ́nà, Ó máa fún igbá-àyà rẹ̀ pa gádígádí bí ẹni pé ó la ìgùnkè lọ sínú sánmọ̀ bọra rẹ̀ lọ́rùn. Báyẹn ni Allāhu ṣe ṣe ìyà fún àwọn tí kò gbàgbọ́.",""
  6,126,"Èyí ni ojú ọ̀nà Olúwa rẹ (tó jẹ́) ọ̀nà tààrà. A kúkú ti ṣàlàyé àwọn āyah fún ìjọ tó ń lo ìrántí.",""
  6,127,"Ilé àlàáfíà ń bẹ fun wọn ní ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa wọn. Òun sì ni Alátìlẹ́yìn wọn nípa ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣe níṣẹ́.",""
  6,128,"(Rántí) Ọjọ́ tí (Allāhu) yóò kó gbogbo wọn jọ pátápátá, (Ó máa sọ pé): “Ẹ̀yin àwùjọ àlùjànnú, dájúdájú ẹ ti kó ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ ènìyàn sọnù.” Àwọn ọ̀rẹ́ wọn nínú àwọn ènìyàn yóò wí pé: “Olúwa wa, apá kan wa gbádùn apá kan ni. A sì ti lo àsìkò wa tí O bù fún wa (láti lò).” (Allāhu) sọ pé: “Iná ni ibùgbé yín; olùṣegbére ni yín nínú rẹ̀ àfi ohun tí Allāhu bá fẹ́<sup>1</sup>. Dájúdájú Olúwa rẹ ni Ọlọ́gbọ́n, Onímọ̀.","[1] Kíyè sí i, āyah yìí kò sọ pé “ إن شاء الله - tí Allāhu bá fẹ́ -.” Ohun tí ó sọ ni pé “إِلَّا مَا شَآءَ - àfi ohun tí Allāhu bá fẹ́ -.”"
  6,129,"Báyẹn ni A ṣe fi apá kan àwọn alábòsí ṣọ̀rẹ́ apá kan (wọn) nítorí ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣe níṣẹ́.",""
  6,130,"Ẹ̀yin àwùjọ àlùjànnú àti ènìyàn, ṣé àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ kan láààrin yín kò wá ba yín, tí wọ́n ń ké àwọn āyah Mi fún yín, tí wọ́n sì ń fi ìpàdé yín Òní yìí ṣèkìlọ̀ fún yín? Wọ́n wí pé: “A jẹ́rìí léra wa lórí (pé wọ́n wá).” Ìṣẹ́mí ayé tàn wọ́n jẹ. Wọ́n sì jẹ́rìí léra wọn lórí pé, dájúdájú àwọn jẹ́ aláìgbàgbọ́.",""
  6,131,"Ìyẹn nítorí pé, Olúwa rẹ kò níí pa àwọn ìlú run nípasẹ̀ àbòsí (ọwọ́ wọn), lásìkò tí àwọn ara ìlú náà jẹ́ aláìmọ̀ (títí Òjíṣẹ́ yóò fi dé bá wọn).",""
